---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import bgImage from "../assets/bg.jpg";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";

const title = "Βρες την ηρεμία σου μεσώ της ψυχοθεραπείας";
const words = title.split(" ");
---

<section
  class="relative flex flex-col items-center min-h-screen text-center px-6 pt-60 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-50"
>
  <Image
    src={bgImage}
    alt="Φόντο ηρεμίας και ψυχοθεραπείας"
    quality="high"
    format="jpg"
    loading="eager"
    fetchpriority="high"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover pointer-events-none animate-slow-zoom"
  />

  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/20 via-transparent to-black/50 z-0 pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <h1
    class="relative z-10 text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-[1.1] max-w-6xl text-neutral-950 font-serif flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-[0.25em]
     gap-y-2"
  >
    {
      words.map((word, i) => (
        <span
          class="inline-block animate-blur-in opacity-0"
          style={`animation-delay: ${0.5 + i * 0.12}s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;`}
        >
          {word === "ψυχοθεραπείας" ? (
            <span class="text-violet-700 italic">{word}</span>
          ) : (
            word
          )}
        </span>
      ))
    }
  </h1>

  <p
    class="relative z-10 mt-6 text-base text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up opacity-0 font-medium"
    style="animation-delay: 1.2s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
  >
    Είτε αντιμετωπίζεις άγχος, κατάθλιψη, είτε απλά θέλεις να κατανοήσεις
    καλύτερα τον εαυτό σου,
    <br />
    είμαστε εδώ για να σε στηρίξουμε σε κάθε βήμα του ταξιδιού σου προς την ευεξία.
  </p>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 mt-5 flex items-center gap-4 animate-fade-in-up opacity-0"
    style="animation-delay: 1.5s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
  >
    <Button href="/quote" variant="primary">Μάθε περισσότερα</Button>
    <Button href="/demo" variant="secondary">Κλείσε ραντεβού</Button>
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 animate-fade-in-up opacity-0"
    style="animation-delay: 2s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
  >
    <span
      class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-white font-bold drop-shadow-[0_4px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]"
    >
      Δες τις υπηρεσιες
    </span>

    <div class="w-[2px] h-14 bg-white/40 relative overflow-hidden rounded-full">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-white animate-scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* New slow zoom animation for the background */
  @keyframes slowZoom {
    from {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    to {
      transform: scale(1.15);
    }
  }

  .animate-slow-zoom {
    /* 20 seconds for a very subtle, professional feel */
    animation: slowZoom 20s ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes blurIn {
    from {
      filter: blur(12px) drop-shadow(0 0 0px rgba(0,0,0,0));
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      filter: blur(0px) drop-shadow(4px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3));
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes scrollLine {
    0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    50%, 100% { transform: translateY(100%); }
  }

  .animate-blur-in {
    animation: blurIn 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }

  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }

  .animate-scroll-line {
    animation: scrollLine 2s cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.35, 1) infinite;
  }
</style>